mahu bunuh Jo Seoktae.

105
00:09:44,588 --> 00:09:46,255
Bagaimana nak dapat waran?

106
00:09:47,338 --> 00:09:50,046
Kita mohon waran untuk serangan
terhadap Cha Yeonho.

107
00:09:50,130 --> 00:09:51,714
Hukumannya dua tahun.

108
00:09:51,797 --> 00:09:55,547
