214
00:16:12,797 --> 00:16:16,505
Mungkin waktu ini dia sedar
kita mengekorinya.

215
00:16:16,588 --> 00:16:18,296
Ke mana dia pergi?

216
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:21,171
Kedai runcit berdekatan,
restoran seolleungtang

217
00:16:21,255 --> 00:16:22,880
dan tiga stesen minyak.

218
00:16:26,213 --> 00:16:29,296
Beli barang runcit di kedai,
makan di restoran

219
00:16:29,380 --> 00:16:31,380
dan isi minyak di stesen minyak.

220
00:16:32,797 --> 00:16:34,338
